---
import dashboardImg from '../assets/image/Dashboard.webp';

const bullets = [
  "Dashboard intuitivo",
  "Módulos integrados",
  "Información actualizada",
  "Fácil de usar",
];

const clients = [
  { name: "MINIMARKET", sub: "Express" },
  { name: "LA PARRILLA", sub: "" },
  { name: "FERRETERÍA", sub: "El Constructor" },
  { name: "BOUTIQUE", sub: "Fashion Store" },
  { name: "FARMACIA", sub: "Salud y Vida" },
  { name: "DISTRIBUIDORA", sub: "Los Amigos" },
  { name: "LA BODEGA", sub: "Desde TRIG" },
  { name: "IMPORTADORA", sub: "Global Peru" },
];
---
<section class="showcase">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="panel reveal">
      <div class="mockup"><img src={dashboardImg.src} alt="Dashboard NANIVA" /></div>
      <div class="info">
        <h2>Todo tu negocio<br />bajo control</h2>
        <p>Visualiza tus ventas, productos, clientes y más en un solo lugar. Información clara para tomar mejores decisiones.</p>
        <ul>
          {bullets.map((b) => (
            <li><span class="check">✓</span>{b}</li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <a href="#demo" class="cta hover-pop">▶ Ver Demo del Sistema →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="clients reveal">
      <h3>Empresas que confían en <span class="brand">NANIVA</span></h3>
      <p class="clients-sub">Más de 1,500 negocios en todo el Perú ya digitalizaron su gestión con nosotros.</p>
      <div class="clients-grid">
        {clients.map((c) => (
          <div class="client">
            <span class="client-name">{c.name}</span>
            {c.sub && <span class="client-sub">{c.sub}</span>}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .showcase { background: white; padding-top: 1.5rem; }
  .showcase .container { max-width: 1500px; }
  .panel {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef4ff, #f5f8ff);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .mockup {
    flex: 3.4;
    min-width: 760px;
    aspect-ratio: 2917 / 1334;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: white;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mockup img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-14px); }
  }
  .info { flex: 1; min-width: 320px; }
  .info h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3.6vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: #0f172a;
  }
  .info p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .info ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }
  .info li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #1e293b;
  }
  .check {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .clients {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .clients h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .brand { color: #2563eb; }
  .clients-sub { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .clients-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .client { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; min-width: 0; }
  .client-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #0f172a;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .clients-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .clients-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  .client-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .mockup { min-width: 100%; flex-basis: 100%; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .panel { padding: 1rem; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .info h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .info p { font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .info li { font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .cta { width: 100%; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem; }
    .clients-grid { gap: 0.75rem; }
  }
</style>
